name: Fifty Eight
description:
According to HEN it'd be the 53rd piece. 
If I trust my 2021 folder, it's closer to 70+.
So what's even the deal with these numbers? 
Truth is...most of my pieces are untitled until they get uploaded.
Sometime a title help, sometime you just zone in on something 
and there's not much to say about it.
I tend to hope pieces like these speak for themselves,
else I just failed somewhere down the line.
